Residents in the area are encouraged to avoid contact with standing water and mud, use protective clothing and [monitor themselves and their pets](https://www.foxnews.com/category/lifestyle/pets) for signs of illness.

Anyone who has been exposed or is experiencing symptoms should seek immediate [medical attention](https://www.foxnews.com/category/health/health-care).

